query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN startDate IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_startdate,
  SUM(CASE WHEN startDate IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_startdate
FROM campaigns;
